## Supplementary Figure 8C-Functional Enrichment Analysis of Core Upregulated Genes

Gene Ontology enrichment analysis of core upregulated genes identified in impaired alveoli.

### Workflow

- Core upregulated genes were identified from differential expression analyses.
- Gene Ontology enrichment analysis was performed using DAVID.
- Significantly enriched biological processes were selected based on adjusted p-values.
- Results were visualized as enrichment bar plots.

### Software

- DAVID Functional Annotation Tool
- GraphPad Prism
